title: Palace Brothers (Will Oldham) and Smog (Bill Callahan) aka The S
description:
Long out of print EP from Will Oldham and Bill Callahan.

I only have these as 192kbps mp3s ripped from the vinyl I'm afraid.

From Wikipedia:

Goat Songs is the name of a 7" vinyl EP by The Sundowners, released on Sea Note Records in 1993. The EP is a collaboration between Palace Brothers (Will Oldham) and Smog (Bill Callahan). The EP was reissued on 21 May 1994. (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Goat_Songs)
